@startuml
' Sequential pattern: Orchestrator drives Planner → Critic → Solver, threading outputs.
' Palette: O=indigo, request=emerald (Send), response=sky (Recv).
skinparam backgroundColor transparent
skinparam defaultFontName Inter
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor #475569
  LifeLineBorderColor #94a3b8
  ParticipantBorderColor #3730a3
  ParticipantBackgroundColor #e0e7ff
  ParticipantFontColor #1e1b4b
}

participant "O\nOrchestrator" as O
participant "P\nPlanner" as P
participant "C\nCritic" as C
participant "S\nSolver" as S

O -[#059669]> P : plan_req
P -[#0284c7]-> O : plan
O -[#059669]> C : critique_req
C -[#0284c7]-> O : critique
O -[#059669]> S : solve_req
S -[#0284c7]-> O : solution
note over O,S : round k's solution threads into round k+1's plan_req (clamp 1..5), then end
@enduml
